videos.headline: Eagles strike first as Fields dives into end zone for TD
videos.description: Georgia Southern RB Wesley Fields takes a pitch and scampers in for an 8-yard score, putting the Eagles ahead 7-0.

videos.headline: Eagles' Richardson takes it 53 yards to the house
videos.description: Georgia Southern QB Shai Werts throws over the middle to Ellis Richardson who outruns the defense to score a 53-yard touchdown, giving the Eagles a 14-0 lead.

videos.headline: Hoggins breaks tackle and breaks free for long Ragin' Cajuns TD
videos.description: Louisiana-Lafayette RB Darius Hoggins spins away from a defender behind the line of scrimmage then takes it down the sideline for a 75-yard score.
